AVR INTERNET SIGN

This project provides the firmware for implementing an ethernet connected
LED sign in an embedded environment. Software is included to drive the LED
display, as well as provide a simple HTTP server for configuration.

PROJECT HARDWARE

The core components of this project are:
- Atmel ATmega328P microcontroller
- WIZnet WIZ811MJ breakout board with embedded W5100 and RJ-45 connector
- SureElectronics DE-DP13112 LED display

